ready for you to try.

Product highlights

Make Code app: We're excited to share the release of Make Code, a built-in =
app that allows you to add arbitrary JavaScript or Python code to your scen=
ario. Learn more ( https://www.make.com/en/blog/make-code-app?utm_campaign=
=3DProduct+Newsletter+10%2F2025&utm_medium=3Demail&utm_source=3Dcustomer.io=
 )

Scenario run replay and naming: Replay scenario runs to test, debug, and ba=
ckfill data faster. You can also customize scenario run names to make your =
scenario history easily readable. Learn more ( https://www.make.com/en/blog=
/scenario-run-replay-naming-rate-limits?utm_campaign=3DProduct+Newsletter+1=
0%2F2025&utm_medium=3Demail&utm_source=3Dcustomer.io )

Scenario sharing experience: You can now easily share your scenarios with o=
thers by generating a public sharing page. No JSONs, just click to share. L=
earn more ( https://www.make.com/en/blog/make-scenario-sharing?utm_campaign=
=3DProduct+Newsletter+10%2F2025&utm_medium=3Demail&utm_source=3Dcustomer.io=
 ) =C2=A0=C2=A0

MCP Server enhancements: Now, your external AI systems and chat interfaces =
can run your scenarios and manage your Make account. Learn more ( https://d=
evelopers.make.com/mcp-server?utm_campaign=3DProduct+Newsletter+10%2F2025&u=
tm_medium=3Demail&utm_source=3Dcustomer.io )

Bring your AI Provider: Use your own AI provider connection for Make AI Age=
nts and other AI apps. Now available on all paid plans!

