New Gmail app: The new Gmail app is now easier to use than ever before. Use=
rs can easily connect to personal Gmail accounts, and use enhanced modules =
like Reply, Search, Send Draft, API Call, and more. Read more ( https://hel=
p.make.com/new-gmail-app-is-now-available?utm_campaign=3DProduct+Newsletter=
+10%2F2025&utm_medium=3Demail&utm_source=3Dcustomer.io )

Create videos with OpenAI app: We=E2=80=99ve natively added Sora 2 model to=
 Make=E2=80=99s OpenAI app. You can now generate videos from text prompts r=
ight inside your scenarios. Read more ( https://www.make.com/en/integration=
